  [Text] Government spokesman Evangelos Venizelos today said 
that the Greek diplomatic service, including representatives at 
the United Nations and with the governments of Balkan countries 
as well as with those that play a role in the Bosnia-Hercegovina 
crisis, are fully mobilized to prevent the participation of 
