  [Text] In Vienna today, 'Abd-al-Jabbar 'Umar al-Duri, under 
secretary of the [Iraqi] Foreign Ministry met separately with 
Dr. Shinon Berg, secretary general of the Austrian Foreign 
Ministry, and Dr. (Hovel Miller), head of the Foreign Ministry's 
