<H3> <TI>   Meets With General Gures </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1703201894 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 2000 
GMT 17 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1703201894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
